# Python Port Plan — Step 03: The Prompt Builder

## Goal

Port `week1_baseline/ruby/03_prompt_builder` to
`week1_baseline/python/03_prompt_builder`. This step adds a `PromptBuilder`
(serializes a `Context` into a backend-specific API payload — no network
calls) and five LLM backend classes (`Anthropic`, `Gemini`, `Ollama`,
`OllamaCloud`, `OpenAI`), each with its own supported-model table and
request/response formatting rules, plus an `UnsupportedModelError`. Same
behavior, same example output shape, same shared `.boukensha/` fixture
directory as the Ruby version.

